 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="49eadbc3-4908-4de4-aed2-356e6c8f7c45" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="81">Ca să ștergi o imagine din GitHub (exact ca în screenshot-ul tău), urmează pașii:</p>
<hr data-start="83" data-end="86">
<h3 data-section-id="12rowf9" data-start="88" data-end="137">🔹 Varianta simplă (din browser – ca în poză)</h3>
<ol data-start="139" data-end="461">
<li data-section-id="lr43yp" data-start="139" data-end="196">
<p data-start="142" data-end="196">Intră în repository-ul tău (unde e folderul <code data-start="186" data-end="195">imagini</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1xonosk" data-start="197" data-end="270">
<p data-start="200" data-end="270">Dă click pe imaginea pe care vrei să o ștergi (ex: <code data-start="251" data-end="269">gel_curatare.jpg</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="a6oe1" data-start="271" data-end="297">
<p data-start="274" data-end="297">Se va deschide fișierul</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="zwqg42" data-start="298" data-end="351">
<p data-start="301" data-end="351">În dreapta sus apasă pe <strong data-start="325" data-end="349">🗑️ Delete this file</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1i9iqxn" data-start="352" data-end="433">
<p data-start="355" data-end="382">Va apărea pagina de commit:</p>
<ul data-start="386" data-end="433">
<li data-section-id="1pjoe8z" data-start="386" data-end="433">
<p data-start="388" data-end="433">la mesaj poți lăsa: <code data-start="408" data-end="433">Delete gel_curatare.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1p04qop" data-start="434" data-end="461">
<p data-start="437" data-end="461">Apasă <strong data-start="443" data-end="461">Commit changes</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="463" data-end="494">✔️ Gata — imaginea este ștearsă</p>
<hr data-start="496" data-end="499">
<h3 data-section-id="1bqak59" data-start="501" data-end="537">🔹 Dacă nu vezi butonul „Delete”</h3>
<p data-start="538" data-end="550">Înseamnă că:</p>
<ul data-start="551" data-end="622">
<li data-section-id="6x2tx8" data-start="551" data-end="588">
<p data-start="553" data-end="588">nu ai permisiuni de editare <strong data-start="581" data-end="588">SAU</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="14tz47q" data-start="589" data-end="622">
<p data-start="591" data-end="622">nu ești logată pe contul corect</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="624" data-end="627">
<h3 data-section-id="evc5wk" data-start="629" data-end="650">🔹 Sfat important</h3>
<p data-start="651" data-end="706">Dacă ai folosit imaginea în site (HTML), după ștergere:</p>
<ul data-start="707" data-end="787">
<li data-section-id="cv660m" data-start="707" data-end="787">
<p data-start="709" data-end="787">trebuie să ștergi și linia din cod (ex: din <code data-start="753" data-end="765">index.html</code>, <code data-start="767" data-end="781">galerie.html</code> etc.)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="789" data-end="797">Exemplu:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="798" data-end="846"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>HTML</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="btn relative group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-width:1.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-offset:2.5px] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-style:solid] group-focus-within/dialog:focus-visible:[outline-color:var(--text-primary)] btn-ghost size-9" aria-label="Редактировать"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-1.5"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-label="" class="-mx-1 