><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="104">Foarte bună întrebare 🔥 — galeria ta acum e goală și trebuie umplută <strong data-start="70" data-end="79">smart</strong>, nu doar cu poze random.</p>
<hr data-start="106" data-end="109">
<h2 data-section-id="1nm4f9i" data-start="111" data-end="167">💡 Ce trebuie să pui în galerie (pentru site ROSELLE)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="14xhr26" data-start="169" data-end="210">🔹 1. Set complet produse (IMPORTANT)</h3>
<p data-start="211" data-end="259">👉 Imaginea pe care ai generat-o acum<br data-start="248" data-end="251">
✔️ Pune:</p>
<ul data-start="260" data-end="316">
<li data-section-id="we871i" data-start="260" data-end="273">
<p data-start="262" data-end="273">set complet</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a4oqmt" data-start="274" data-end="295">
<p data-start="276" data-end="295">set mic (3 produse)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="eqmxwh" data-start="296" data-end="316">
<p data-start="298" data-end="316">set cu fundal blur</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="318" data-end="321">
<h3 data-section-id="1ho1epd" data-start="323" data-end="366">🔹 2. Fiecare produs separat (close-up)</h3>
<p data-start="367" data-end="370">Ex:</p>
<ul data-start="371" data-end="469">
<li data-section-id="1ybm1oo" data-start="371" data-end="389">
<p data-start="373" data-end="389">cremă hidratantă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wfrl8u" data-start="390" data-end="406">
<p data-start="392" data-end="406">ser vitamina C</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1yfp424" data-start="407" data-end="421">
<p data-start="409" data-end="421">gel curățare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gjiup0" data-start="422" data-end="436">
<p data-start="424" data-end="436">apă micelară</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lv3agr" data-start="437" data-end="453">
<p data-start="439" data-end="453">loțiune tonică</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1641ff8" data-start="454" data-end="469">
<p data-start="456" data-end="469">mască facială</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="471" data-end="479">✔️ Stil:</p>
<ul data-start="480" data-end="524">
<li data-section-id="1rpioe6" data-start="480" data-end="497">
<p data-start="482" data-end="497">focus pe produs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="yj0f97" data-start="498" data-end="510">
<p data-start="500" data-end="510">fundal roz</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tomgqe" data-start="511" data-end="524">
<p data-start="513" data-end="524">lumină soft</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="526" data-end="529">
<h3 data-section-id="16jmkvg" data-start="531" data-end="581">🔹 3. Lifestyle / utilizare (foarte important)</h3>
<p data-start="582" data-end="609">👉 Face site-ul PROFESIONAL</p>
<p data-start="611" data-end="619">Exemple:</p>
<ul data-start="620" data-end="706">
<li data-section-id="zyw1vx" data-start="620" data-end="637">
<p data-start="622" data-end="637">produs + prosop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1045jq4" data-start="638" data-end="663">
<p data-start="640" data-end="663">produs + apă (picături)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8bzbja" data-start="664" data-end="689">
<p data-start="666" data-end="689">produs pe masă cu flori</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bml0zs" data-start="690" data-end="706">
<p data-start="692" data-end="706">produs în baie</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="708" data-end="711">
<h3 data-section-id="12o55fh" data-start="713" data-end="745">🔹 4. Detalii (premium look)</h3>
<p data-start="746" data-end="757">✔️ Zoom pe:</p>
<ul data-start="758" data-end="804">
<li data-section-id="32jqkr" data-start="758" data-end="773">
<p data-start="760" data-end="773">textură cremă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z23bzw" data-start="774" data-end="794">
<p data-start="776" data-end="794">picături pe sticlă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="m64qqo" data-start="795" data-end="804">
<p data-start="797" data-end="804">ambalaj</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="806" data-end="809">
<h3 data-section-id="pk9sf9" data-start="811" data-end="850">🔹 5. Seturi promo (pentru vânzare)</h3>
<p data-start="851" data-end="854">Ex:</p>
