<hr data-start="93" data-end="96">
<h1 data-section-id="11d1002" data-start="98" data-end="121">💡 Diferența corectă:</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="quxk0j" data-start="123" data-end="145">🛒 Pagina „Produse”</h2>
<p data-start="146" data-end="157">✔ aici pui:</p>
<ul data-start="158" data-end="206">
<li data-section-id="nup3cj" data-start="158" data-end="178">
<p data-start="160" data-end="178">poze simple, clare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="2u6u21" data-start="179" data-end="206">
<p data-start="181" data-end="206">focus pe produs (vânzare)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="208" data-end="230">👉 exact ce ai deja ✔️</p>
<hr data-start="232" data-end="235">
<h2 data-section-id="1kn1t0p" data-start="237" data-end="260">🖼️ Pagina „Galerie”</h2>
<p data-start="261" data-end="272">✔ aici pui:</p>
<ul data-start="273" data-end="378">
<li data-section-id="j6rmig" data-start="273" data-end="308">
<p data-start="275" data-end="308">poze <strong data-start="280" data-end="308">mai artistice / estetice</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="w2ro3t" data-start="309" data-end="342">
<p data-start="311" data-end="342">NU aceleași imagini din produse</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="t51lxa" data-start="343" data-end="378">
<p data-start="345" data-end="378">scop: <strong data-start="351" data-end="378">branding + impresie WOW</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="380" data-end="383">
<h1 data-section-id="1c4k83k" data-start="385" data-end="427">🔥 Ce trebuie să pui în galerie (corect)</h1>
<h3 data-section-id="1ottwyz" data-start="429" data-end="438">❌ NU:</h3>
<ul data-start="439" data-end="486">
<li data-section-id="wqykim" data-start="439" data-end="466">
<p data-start="441" data-end="466">aceleași poze din produse</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="62auoj" data-start="467" data-end="486">
<p data-start="469" data-end="486">imagini duplicate</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="488" data-end="491">
<h3 data-section-id="1nef18c" data-start="493" data-end="502">✅ DA:</h3>
<h2 data-section-id="172spkx" data-start="504" data-end="529">1. Seturi (compoziții)</h2>
<ul data-start="530" data-end="578">
<li data-section-id="d2ef8e" data-start="530" data-end="558">
<p data-start="532" data-end="558">mai multe produse împreună</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="c7d7fm" data-start="559" data-end="578">
<p data-start="561" data-end="578">diferite aranjări</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="580" data-end="607">👉 tu deja ai (foarte bine)</p>
<hr data-start="609" data-end="612">
<h2 data-section-id="h4wjxb" data-start="614" data-end="634">2. Poze artistice</h2>
<ul data-start="635" data-end="686">
<li data-section-id="fl1rp1" data-start="635" data-end="651">
<p data-start="637" data-end="651">blur în fundal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tomgqe" data-start="652" data-end="665">
<p data-start="654" data-end="665">lumină soft</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="152h6xz" data-start="666" data-end="686">
<p data-start="668" data-end="686">focus pe atmosferă</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="688" data-end="691">
<h2 data-section-id="12i5i7d" data-start="693" data-end="708">3. Lifestyle</h2>
<ul data-start="709" data-end="771">
<li data-section-id="zyw1vx" data-start="709" data-end="726">
<p data-start="711" data-end="726">produs + prosop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="147ij0y" data-start="727" data-end="752">
<p data-start="729" data-end="752">produs + apă / picături</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12wf8bv" data-start="753" data-end="771">
<p data-start="755" data-end="771">produs „în baie”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="773" data-end="776">
<h2 data-section-id="3a0whk" data-start="778" data-end="802">4. Close-up (detalii)</h2>
<ul data-start="803" data-end="851">
<li data-section-id="1g9ghl2" data-start="803" data-end="819">
<p data-start="805" data-end="819">textura cremei</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z23bzw" data-start="820" data-end="840">
<p data-start="822" data-end="840">picături pe sticlă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xe83vs" data-start="841" data-end="851">
<p data-start="843" data-end="851">reflexii</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="853" data-end="856">
<h2 data-section-id="3wyr2k" data-start="858" data-end="882">5. Promo (brand look)</h2>
<ul data-start="883" data-end="922">
<li data-section-id="18csztd" data-start="883" data-end="900">
<p data-start="885" data-end="900">seturi elegante</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="47ga1m" data-start="901" data-end="922">
<p data-start="903" data-end="922">poziționare premium</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="924" data-end="927">
<h1 data-section-id="1mx0ddg" data-start="929" data-end="946">🎯 Simplu spus:</h1>
<p data-start="948" data-end="1020">👉 <strong data-start="951" data-end="972">Produse = vânzare</strong><br data-start="972" data-end="975">
👉 <strong data-start="978" data-end="1020">Galerie = marketing / imagine de brand</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1022" data-end="1025">
<h1 data-section-id="1x08hx2" data-start="1027" data-end="1067">💅 Exemplu ideal pentru tine (ROSELLE)</h1>
<p data-start="1069" data-end="1085">În galerie pune:</p>
<ol data-start="1086" data-end="1258">
<li data-section-id="ymqrgu" data-start="1086" data-end="1107">
<p data-start="1089" data-end="1107">Set complet (mare)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13g0kro" data-start="1108" data-end="1130">
<p data-start="1111" data-end="1130">Set mic (3 produse)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="os8wpd" data-start="1131" data-end="1155">
<p data-start="1134" data-end="1155">Set cu blur în fundal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12hpnd7" data-start="1156" data-end="1183">
<p data-start="1159" data-end="1183">Toner + mască (artistic)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1qmk81m" data-start="1184" data-end="1201">
<p data-start="1187" data-end="1201">Close-up cremă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9tvr8l" data-start="1202" data-end="1220">
<p data-start="1205" data-end="1220">Picături pe gel</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="xio65n" data-start="1221" data-end="1239">
<p data-start="1224" data-end="1239">Produs + floare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19hnxkm" data-start="1240" data-end="1258">
<p data-start="1243" data-end="1258">Produs + prosop</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1260" data-end="1279">✔️ 8–10 imagini MAX</p>
<hr data-start="1281" data-end="1284">
<h1 data-section-id="1ieymnk" data-start="1286" data-end="1300">🔥 Concluzie</h1>
<p data-start="1301" data-end="1371">Nu dubla pozele — altfel site-ul pare:<br>
❌ neprofesional<br data-start="1355" data-end="1358">
❌ repetitiv</p>
<hr data-start="1373" data-end="1376">
<h2 data-section-id="1yqpg7p" data-start="1378" data-end="1393">🚀 Dacă vrei</h2>
<p data-start="1394" data-end="1496">Pot să-ți aleg exact din imaginile generate:<br>
👉 <strong data-start="1442" data-end="1496">8 poze perfecte pentru galerie (premium selection)</strong></p>
