k:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-69d493ff-4794-8332-96e8-23a477540cf4-27" data-testid="conversation-turn-60" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT сказал:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="66145dcd-c313-4d54-9c68-915fa6764689" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="80">Întrebare foarte bună 👏 — asta deja ține de <strong data-start="45" data-end="63">UX + marketing</strong>, nu doar de cod.</p>
<hr data-start="82" data-end="85">
<h1 data-section-id="11m7tgw" data-start="87" data-end="121">🎯 💡 Scopul galeriei (pe scurt)</h1>
<p data-start="123" data-end="199">👉 <strong data-start="126" data-end="153">Galeria NU vinde direct</strong><br data-start="153" data-end="156">
👉 <strong data-start="159" data-end="199">Galeria creează dorință și încredere</strong></p>
<hr data-start="201" data-end="204">
<h1 data-section-id="13uok4k" data-start="206" data-end="227">🔥 Explicat simplu:</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="14bfqrr" data-start="229" data-end="254">🛒 Produse = „CUMPĂRĂ”</h2>
<ul data-start="255" data-end="298">
<li data-section-id="2vg8b8" data-start="255" data-end="266">
<p data-start="257" data-end="266">vezi preț</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="h3gzm8" data-start="267" data-end="283">
<p data-start="269" data-end="283">vezi descriere</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jj2lz5" data-start="284" data-end="298">
<p data-start="286" data-end="298">alegi produs</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="300" data-end="303">
<h2 data-section-id="19920ij" data-start="305" data-end="330">🖼️ Galerie = „WOW 😍”</h2>
<ul data-start="331" data-end="395">
<li data-section-id="50fj2s" data-start="331" data-end="355">
<p data-start="333" data-end="355">vezi cum arată brandul</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rzdk75" data-start="356" data-end="371">
<p data-start="358" data-end="371">simți vibe-ul</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="p1j6mn" data-start="372" data-end="395">
<p data-start="374" data-end="395">îți dorești produsele</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="397" data-end="400">
<h1 data-section-id="ys5ah7" data-start="402" data-end="438">💅 Pentru ROSELLE (brand cosmetic)</h1>
<p data-start="440" data-end="469">Galeria trebuie să transmită:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1ar0dsd" data-start="471" data-end="488">✨ 1. Eleganță</h3>
<ul data-start="489" data-end="514">
<li data-section-id="1ljshxv" data-start="489" data-end="514">
<p data-start="491" data-end="514">culori roz, lumină soft</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1rn1fyd" data-start="516" data-end="548">💧 2. Curățenie / prospețime</h3>
<ul data-start="549" data-end="569">
<li data-section-id="22sviv" data-start="549" data-end="569">
<p data-start="551" data-end="569">apă, picături, gel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1shjxaz" data-start="571" data-end="591">🌸 3. Feminitate</h3>
<ul data-start="592" data-end="615">
<li data-section-id="1t3aak0" data-start="592" data-end="615">
<p data-start="594" data-end="615">flori, piele, texturi</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="5c2nm6" data-start="617" data-end="643">🧴 4. Calitate premium</h3>
<ul data-start="644" data-end="663">
<li data-section-id="1xx02si" data-start="644" data-end="663">
<p data-start="646" data-end="663">detalii, close-up</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="665" data-end="668">
<h1 data-section-id="1yytmpq" data-start="670" data-end="697">🧠 Psihologia (important)</h1>
<p data-start="699" data-end="710">👉 Oamenii:</p>
<ul data-start="711" data-end="764">
<li data-section-id="x430qs" data-start="711" data-end="741">
<p data-start="713" data-end="741"><strong data-start="713" data-end="741">nu cumpără doar produsul</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1co38wx" data-start="742" data-end="764">
<p data-start="744" data-end="764">cumpără <strong data-start="752" data-end="764">senzația</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="766" data-end="769">Ex:</p>
<ul data-start="770" data-end="821">
<li data-section-id="lckyik" data-start="770" data-end="784">
<p data-start="772" data-end="784">„piele fină”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tzp6h6" data-start="785" data-end="801">
<p data-start="787" data-end="801">„aspect curat”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11u3zvl" data-start="802" data-end="821">
<p data-start="804" data-end="821">„lux / self-care”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="823" data-end="843">👉 asta face GALERIA</p>
<hr data-start="845" data-end="848">
<h1 data-section-id="1atm8xg" data-start="850" data-end="873">📈 De ce e importantă</h1>
<p data-start="875" data-end="982">✔ crește încrederea<br data-start="894" data-end="897">
✔ face site-ul profesional<br data-start="923" data-end="926">
