gin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="1a9d3542-a845-4611-8318-7e0eec8c1cd7" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-4-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="10">Fă simplu:</p>
<p data-start="12" data-end="107"><strong data-start="12" data-end="50">Lasă pagina Produse pentru vânzare</strong> și fă <strong data-start="57" data-end="68">Galeria</strong> doar pentru imagini frumoase de brand.</p>
<p data-start="109" data-end="139">Pune în galerie doar 6–8 poze:</p>
<ul data-start="140" data-end="316">
<li data-section-id="h6brdw" data-start="140" data-end="161">
<p data-start="142" data-end="161">un set ROSELLE mare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="inatg8" data-start="162" data-end="177">
<p data-start="164" data-end="177">cremă pe față</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1s9lvwx" data-start="178" data-end="191">
<p data-start="180" data-end="191">gel pe mână</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uut4ad" data-start="192" data-end="208">
<p data-start="194" data-end="208">gel care curge</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rp8mq8" data-start="209" data-end="226">
<p data-start="211" data-end="226">picături pe gel</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="d0hns5" data-start="227" data-end="258">
<p data-start="229" data-end="258">un close-up artistic cu serul</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dbddmo" data-start="259" data-end="290">
<p data-start="261" data-end="290">un close-up artistic cu crema</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gzbk8p" data-start="291" data-end="316">
<p data-start="293" data-end="316">un set mic cu 3 produse</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="318" data-end="331">Ordinea bună:</p>
<ol data-start="332" data-end="406">
<li data-section-id="1l9803" data-start="332" data-end="343">
<p data-start="335" data-end="343">set mare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16o5zqm" data-start="344" data-end="364">
<p data-start="347" data-end="364">poze cu utilizare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12qf9ur" data-start="365" data-end="386">
<p data-start="368" data-end="386">texturi și detalii</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4q5ym3" data-start="387" data-end="406">
<p data-start="390" data-end="406">set mic la final</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="408" data-end="464">Dacă nu vrei să te complici, folosește layout-ul acesta:</p>
<ul data-start="465" data-end="555">
<li data-section-id="t6r9ug" data-start="465" data-end="502">
<p data-start="467" data-end="502">prima imagine mare pe toată lățimea</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10idy9i" data-start="503" data-end="521">
<p data-start="505" data-end="521">sub ea 2 imagini</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hgd5cw" data-start="522" data-end="538">
<p data-start="524" data-end="538">apoi 3 imagini</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gvjsyp" data-start="539" data-end="555">
<p data-start="541" data-end="555">apoi 2 imagini</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="557" data-end="563">Adică:</p>
<ul data-start="564" data-end="735">
<li data-section-id="1tpynih" data-start="564" data-end="586">
<p data-start="566" data-end="586">sus: <strong data-start="571" data-end="586">set complet</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1jrmjwc" data-start="587" data-end="632">
<p data-start="589" data-end="632">mijloc: <strong data-start="597" data-end="614">crema pe față</strong> + <strong data-start="617" data-end="632">gel pe mână</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ltdb29" data-start="633" data-end="694">
<p data-start="635" data-end="694">sub: <strong data-start="640" data-end="653">gel curge</strong> + <strong data-start="656" data-end="675">picături pe gel</strong> + <strong data-start="678" data-end="694">ser artistic</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1halfjk" data-start="695" data-end="735">
<p data-start="697" data-end="735">jos: <strong data-start="702" data-end="713">set mic</strong> + <strong data-start="716" data-end="735">cremă artistică</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="737" data-end="747">Important:</p>
<ul data-start="748" data-end="877">
<li data-section-id="1m2eet1" data-start="748" data-end="798">
<p data-start="750" data-end="798">nu pune aceleași poze ca la cardurile de produse</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="hbqn5e" data-start="799" data-end="827">
<p data-start="801" data-end="827">nu pune prea multe imagini</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13l3loz" data-start="828" data-end="877">
<p data-start="830" data-end="877">toate să fie în același stil roz, soft, premium</p>
</li>
</ul>
