lass="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip rtl:origin-top-right" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full flex-row items-start justify-between gap-4 text-start"><button type="button" class="flex min-w-0 shrink-1 gap-0.5 items-center"><span class="font-medium w-full"><span class="flex gap-1 text-start align-middle items-center truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary dark:hover:text-token-text-primary dark:text-[var(--interactive-label-tertiary-default)]" style="opacity: 1;"><span class="flex min-w-0 gap-1 items-center"><span class="min-w-0 truncate">Думал</span></span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="icon-xs"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#b140e7" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></span></button></div></div><div class="max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))]"></div></div></div><p class="first:mt-0 my-1.5 h-8 flex items-center ltr:me-auto rtl:ms-auto empty:hidden text-token-text-secondary"></p><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="a59a54c3-51d3-40e7-afd7-8a754ca6d7c1" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-4-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="361">Da — la galeria ta trebuie schimbat layout-ul, nu tot site-ul. În CSS-ul tău deja există <code data-start="89" data-end="104">.gallery-grid</code>, <code data-start="106" data-end="121">.gallery-item</code>, <code data-start="123" data-end="139">.gallery-photo</code>, deci e ușor de transformat într-un look premium. În plus, la finalul fișierului ai și o problemă de structură: media query-ul de la <code data-start="273" data-end="300">@media (max-width: 768px)</code> nu este închis corect. <span class="relative inline-flex items-center select-none" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_r_1io_" data-state="closed"><button type="button" class="ms-1 relative flex h-[25px] select-none items-center justify-center gap-1 rounded-xl px-2 text-[10px] leading-[13px] corner-superellipse/1.1 text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">Вставленный текст</p></button></span></p>
<p data-start="363" data-end="408">Înlocuiește partea pentru galerie cu aceasta:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="410" data-end="1855"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>  text-align: </span><span class="ͼq">center</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">40</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h1</span><span> {</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">42</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  font-weight: </span><span class="ͼq">500</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">10</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-hero</span><span> .</span><span class="ͼs">subtitle</span><span> {</span><br><span>  max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">700</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">auto</span><span>;</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--muted</span><span>);</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">16</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* galerie premium */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-grid</span><span> {</span><br><span>  margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">30</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  display: </span><span class="ͼq">grid</span><span>;</span><br><span>  grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">12</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>);</span><br><span>  gap: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* card general */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span> {</span><br><span>  overflow: </span><span class="ͼq">hidden</span><span>;</span><br><span>  border: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--line</span><span>);</span><br><span>  border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  background: </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--surface</span><span>);</span><br><span>  box-shadow: </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--shadow</span><span>);</span><br><span>  transition: </span><span class="ͼq">transform</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.3</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">ease</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">box-shadow</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.3</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">ease</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>  transform: </span><span class="ͼn">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">-6</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>);</span><br><span>  box-shadow: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">36</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">rgba</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">0.10</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* imagine */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-photo</span><span> {</span><br><span>  width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>  height: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>  min-height: </span><span class="ͼq">260</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  max-height: </span><span class="ͼq">520</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  object-fit: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>  display: </span><span class="ͼq">block</span><span>;</span><br><span>  transition: </span><span class="ͼq">transform</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">0.45</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">ease</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-photo</span><span> {</span><br><span>  transform: </span><span class="ͼn">scale</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">1.05</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* text sub imagine */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-info</span><span> {</span><br><span>  padding: </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-info</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h3</span><span> {</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">8</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--text</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-info</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">p</span><span> {</span><br><span>  color: </span><span class="ͼn">var</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼt">--muted</span><span>);</span><br><span>  margin: </span><span class="ͼq">0</span><span>;</span><br><span>  font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">15</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  line-height: </span><span class="ͼq">1.6</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼl">/* layout premium pe coloane */</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span> {</span><br><span>  grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">12</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">large</span><span> {</span><br><span>  grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">6</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">medium</span><span> {</span><br><span>  grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">4</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">small</span><span> {</span><br><span>  grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">3</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1857" data-end="1888">Apoi pune responsive-ul acesta:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1890" data-end="2390"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼn">@media</span><span> (max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">900</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>) {</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-grid</span><span> {</span><br><span>    grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>);</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">large</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">medium</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">small</span><span> {</span><br><span>    grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-photo</span><span> {</span><br><span>    min-height: </span><span class="ͼq">240</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    max-height: </span><span class="ͼq">360</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">@media</span><span> (max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">600</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>) {</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-grid</span><span> {</span><br><span>    grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-photo</span><span> {</span><br><span>    min-height: </span><span class="ͼq">220</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    max-height: </span><span class="ͼq">320</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-hero</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h1</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">32</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2392" data-end="2656">Și foarte important: la finalul fișierului tău CSS adaugă acolada lipsă <code data-start="2464" data-end="2467">}</code> ca să se închidă corect media query-ul. Acum la final ai rămas cu <code data-start="2534" data-end="2558">.product-photo { ... }</code> pus în interiorul media query-ului fără închidere completă. <span class="relative inline-flex items-center select-none" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_r_1ir_" data-state="closed"><button type="button" class="ms-1 relative flex h-[25px] select-none items-center justify-center gap-1 rounded-xl px-2 text-[10px] leading-[13px] corner-superellipse/1.1 text-token-text-secondary! hover:text-token-text-primary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary bg-[#f4f4f4] "><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain text-token-text-primary! flex-none icon-sm"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#554074" fill="currentColor"></use></svg><p class="not-prose mt-0! mb-0! flex-auto truncate">Вставленный текст</p></button></span></p>
<p data-start="2658" data-end="2756">Ca să arate exact premium, în <code data-start="2688" data-end="2702">galerie.html</code> imaginile trebuie puse cu clase diferite, de exemplu:</p>
