class="ͼq">1</span><span>;</span><br><span>    min-height: </span><span class="ͼq">300</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">hero-card</span><span> {</span><br><span>    min-height: </span><span class="ͼq">360</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-overlay</span><span> {</span><br><span>    left: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    right: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    bottom: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>    max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">none</span><span>;</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">18</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-overlay</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h2</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">34</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">quote-big</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">48</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼn">@media</span><span> (max-width: </span><span class="ͼq">600</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>) {</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-gallery</span><span> {</span><br><span>    grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">hero-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">small-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">text-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">medium-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">quote-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">large-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">wide-card</span><span> {</span><br><span>    grid-column: </span><span class="ͼq">span</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">text-card</span><span>,</span><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">quote-card</span><span> {</span><br><span>    padding: </span><span class="ͼq">24</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><br><span>  .</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-overlay</span><span> </span><span class="ͼv">h2</span><span> {</span><br><span>    font-size: </span><span class="ͼq">28</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  }</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="6476" data-end="6479">
<h1 data-section-id="149wm95" data-start="6481" data-end="6509">Какие фото лучше поставить</h1>
<p data-start="6511" data-end="6524">Примерно так:</p>
<ul data-start="6526" data-end="6748">
<li data-section-id="1p56hfo" data-start="6526" data-end="6550">
<p data-start="6528" data-end="6550"><code data-start="6528" data-end="6536">p1.jpg</code> → set ROSELLE</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1weurp7" data-start="6551" data-end="6577">
<p data-start="6553" data-end="6577"><code data-start="6553" data-end="6561">p2.jpg</code> → cremă pe față</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1t53fkj" data-start="6578" data-end="6602">
<p data-start="6580" data-end="6602"><code data-start="6580" data-end="6588">p3.jpg</code> → gel pe mână</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dup5c5" data-start="6603" data-end="6625">
<p data-start="6605" data-end="6625"><code data-start="6605" data-end="6613">p4.jpg</code> → gel curge</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="sa4wlw" data-start="6626" data-end="6654">
<p data-start="6628" data-end="6654"><code data-start="6628" data-end="6636">p5.jpg</code> → picături pe gel</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="itqnmw" data-start="6655" data-end="6680">
<p data-start="6657" data-end="6680"><code data-start="6657" data-end="6665">p6.jpg</code> → ser artistic</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="td8sqz" data-start="6681" data-end="6701">
<p data-start="6683" data-end="6701"><code data-start="6683" data-end="6691">p7.jpg</code> → set mic</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tl7kom" data-start="6702" data-end="6748">
<p data-start="6704" data-end="6748"><code data-start="6704" data-end="6712">p8.jpg</code> → close-up cremă sau produs premium</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="6750" data-end="6753">
<h1 data-section-id="1hsfgoj" data-start="6755" data-end="6792">Почему это будет похоже на референс</h1>
<p data-start="6794" data-end="6815">Потому что получится:</p>
<ul data-start="6816" data-end="6933">
<li data-section-id="1uot5gr" data-start="6816" data-end="6840">
<p data-start="6818" data-end="6840">крупный верхний баннер</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ru4g4e" data-start="6841" data-end="6863">
<p data-start="6843" data-end="6863">шахматная композиция</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="nzqdty" data-start="6864" data-end="6889">
<p data-start="6866" data-end="6889">большие editorial блоки</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fmikiv" data-start="6890" data-end="6915">
<p data-start="6892" data-end="6915">сочетание фото и текста</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1v6dhn3" data-start="6916" data-end="6933">
<p data-start="6918" data-end="6933">luxury ощущение</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="6935" data-end="6947">Но при этом:</p>
<ul data-start="6948" data-end="7038">
<li data-section-id="mv2ui0" data-start="6948" data-end="6967">
<p data-start="6950" data-end="6967">в <strong data-start="6952" data-end="6967">твоем стиле</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1tk4u8c" data-start="6968" data-end="6985">
<p data-start="6970" data-end="6985">розовая палитра</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="92ehbf" data-start="6986" data-end="7001">
<p data-start="6988" data-end="7001">skincare mood</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="116ehn6" data-start="7002" data-end="7038">
<p data-start="7004" data-end="7038">мягкость, femininity, clean beauty</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="7040" data-end="7212" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Если хочешь, я могу сразу сделать тебе еще и <strong data-start="7085" data-end="7185">полностью готовую финальную версию <code data-start="7122" data-end="7136">galerie.html</code> + <code data-start="7139" data-end="7150">style.css</code> под твои конкретные фото <code data-start="7176" data-end="7183">p1–p8</code></strong>, чтобы ты просто вставила.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Действия с ответом" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Копировать ответ" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Хороший ответ" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center to