<hr data-start="117" data-end="120">
<h2 data-section-id="hb71qs" data-start="122" data-end="154">🔥 SOLUȚIA RAPIDĂ (în 2 pași)</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1vf2zwe" data-start="156" data-end="213"><span role="text">✅ 1. În <code data-start="168" data-end="179">style.css</code> — șterge TOT ce ține de editorial</span></h3>
<p data-start="215" data-end="239">Caută și șterge complet:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="241" data-end="490"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-gallery</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-img</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">hero-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">small-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">text-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">medium-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">quote-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">large-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">wide-card</span><span> { ... }</span><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">editorial-overlay</span><span> { ... }</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="492" data-end="538">👉 dacă vrei simplu: șterge tot blocul dintre:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="539" data-end="590"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>/* ===== ROSELLE EDITORIAL GALLERY ===== */</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="592" data-end="595">
<h3 data-section-id="3864gl" data-start="597" data-end="651">✅ 2. Adaugă la finalul CSS-ului (FOARTE IMPORTANT)</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="653" data-end="1079"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>CSS</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Копировать" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-dd80ba6x.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼl">/* FIX GALERIE NORMALA */</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-grid</span><span> {</span><br><span>  display: </span><span class="ͼq">grid</span><span> </span><span class="ͼn">!important</span><span>;</span><br><span>  grid-template-columns: </span><span class="ͼn">repeat</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">4</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">fr</span><span>) </span><span class="ͼn">!important</span><span>;</span><br><span>  gap: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  margin-top: </span><span class="ͼq">20</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span> {</span><br><span>  background: </span><span class="ͼq">white</span><span>;</span><br><span>  border-radius: </span><span class="ͼq">16</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  overflow: </span><span class="ͼq">hidden</span><span>;</span><br><span>  border: </span><span class="ͼq">1</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span> </span><span class="ͼq">solid</span><span> #eee;</span><br><span>  transition: </span><span class="ͼq">0.3</span><span class="ͼn">s</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-item</span><span>:</span><span class="ͼs">hover</span><span> {</span><br><span>  transform: </span><span class="ͼn">translateY</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼq">-5</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>);</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span>.</span><span class="ͼs">gallery-photo</span><span> {</span><br><span>  width: </span><span class="ͼq">100</span><span class="ͼn">%</span><span>;</span><br><span>  height: </span><span class="ͼq">220</span><span class="ͼn">px</span><span>;</span><br><span>  object-fit: </span><span class="ͼq">cover</span><span>;</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1081" data-end="1084">
<h3 data-section-id="19a3f7x" data-start="1086" data-end="1119">✅ 3. HTML-ul tău este OK ✔️</h3>
