<h2 data-section-id="1s1dycl" data-start="47" data-end="84">🔍 Ce NU e ok în imaginea generată</h2>
<p data-start="86" data-end="144">👉 Nu este 100% în stilul tău original ROSELLE, pentru că:</p>
<ol data-start="146" data-end="538">
<li data-section-id="1axnb8d" data-start="146" data-end="306">
<p data-start="149" data-end="172"><strong data-start="149" data-end="172">Logo-ul nu e corect</strong></p>
<ul data-start="176" data-end="306">
<li data-section-id="1bp1jl9" data-start="176" data-end="240">
<p data-start="178" data-end="240">apare „ROSELLE”, dar fontul și stilul nu sunt exact ca la tine</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1nexmiv" data-start="244" data-end="306">
<p data-start="246" data-end="306">unele produse au texte greșite („ROSEALLE”, „HODRELLE” etc.)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cvd4yo" data-start="308" data-end="427">
<p data-start="311" data-end="346"><strong data-start="311" data-end="346">Design-ul ambalajelor e diferit</strong></p>
<ul data-start="350" data-end="427">
<li data-section-id="t4pbz9" data-start="350" data-end="383">
<p data-start="352" data-end="383">la tine: simplu, curat, minimal</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rhfzpe" data-start="387" data-end="427">
<p data-start="389" data-end="427">aici: prea „luxury random”, nu uniform</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5xumh2" data-start="429" data-end="538">
<p data-start="432" data-end="464"><strong data-start="432" data-end="464">Produsele nu sunt cele reale</strong></p>
<ul data-start="468" data-end="538">
<li data-section-id="c8hcha" data-start="468" data-end="509">
<p data-start="470" data-end="509">ai în site: gel, ser, cremă, mască etc.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9dbog4" data-start="513" data-end="538">
<p data-start="515" data-end="538">aici: produse inventate</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="540" data-end="543">
<h2 data-section-id="1bqy1sg" data-start="545" data-end="565">✅ Ce e totuși bun</h2>
<p data-start="567" data-end="648">✔ culorile (roz, rose gold)<br data-start="594" data-end="597">
✔ atmosfera (soft, feminin)<br data-start="624" data-end="627">
✔ ideea de set mare</p>
<hr data-start="650" data-end="653">
<h2 data-section-id="96w2m1" data-start="655" data-end="687">💯 Ce trebuie să facem corect</h2>
<p data-start="689" data-end="705">Tu ai nevoie de:</p>
<p data-start="707" data-end="758">👉 <strong data-start="710" data-end="749">SET REAL ROSELLE (brand consistent)</strong><br data-start="749" data-end="752">
adică:</p>
<ul data-start="759" data-end="846">
<li data-section-id="40ouwn" data-start="759" data-end="797">
<p data-start="761" data-end="797">aceleași produse ca pe site-ul tău</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1m8tui4" data-start="798" data-end="824">
<p data-start="800" data-end="824">același font „ROSELLE”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1k0q1bu" data-start="825" data-end="846">
<p data-start="827" data-end="846">aceleași ambalaje</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="848" data-end="851">
<h2 data-section-id="1uza344" data-start="853" data-end="874">🔥 Soluția corectă</h2>
<p data-start="876" data-end="927">Pot să-ți generez o imagine PERFECTĂ dacă îmi spui:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="229six" data-start="929" data-end="950">✔ vrei să includ:</h3>
<ul data-start="951" data-end="1070">
<li data-section-id="1dkk40d" data-start="951" data-end="968">
<p data-start="953" data-end="968">gel de curățare</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wfrl8u" data-start="969" data-end="985">
<p data-start="971" data-end="985">ser vitamina C</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ybm1oo" data-start="986" data-end="1004">
<p data-start="988" data-end="1004">cremă hidratantă</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hcsfiq" data-start="1005" data-end="1022">
<p data-start="1007" data-end="1022">cremă de noapte</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1gjiup0" data-start="1023" data-end="1037">
<p data-start="1025" data-end="1037">apă micelară</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lv3agr" data-start="1038" data-end="1054">
<p data-start="1040" data-end="1054">loțiune tonică</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1641ff8" data-start="1055" data-end="1070">
<p data-start="1057" data-end="1070">mască facială</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1072" data-end="1075">
<h2 data-section-id="cxw2ec" data-start="1077" data-end="1112">✨ Și o fac EXACT ca brandul tău:</h2>
<ul data-start="1113" data-end="1231">
<li data-section-id="ehowwg" data-start="1113" data-end="1150">
<p data-start="1115" data-end="1150">același stil ca imaginile tale ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="126o85o" data-start="1151" data-end="1178">
<p data-start="1153" data-end="1178">același logo ROSELLE ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z7iqmm" data-start="1179" data-end="1204">
<p data-start="1181" data-end="1204">fără texte greșite ✔️</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hkoev7" data-start="1205" data-end="1231">
<p data-start="1207" data-end="1231">perfect pentru site ✔️</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1233" data-end="1236">
<p data-start="1238" data-end="1290">👉 Scrie doar:<br>
<strong data-start="1253" data-end="1290">„da, toate produsele + stil site”</strong></p>
